    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle is a smart choice for a buyer who values affordability and straightforward ownership. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking practical everyday use, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. Offered honestly and priced to deliver strong value, it represents a cost-effective way to get behind the wheel without overcommitting.",
