      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It\u2019s got the kind of honest character you expect from a well-used vehicle, and for the right buyer it could be a smart, practical pickup without spending a fortune. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and full of potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great fundamentals and plenty of upside for the next owner. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of honest mechanical character enthusiasts look for in a driver-level build. Shows age cosmetically and will benefit from ongoing TLC, but it presents as a usable, complete car with a strong platform for restoration, weekend duty, or a budget performance-minded setup. Priced to move for someone who appreciates a wrench-friendly car with real potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    }
